```

## Conventions

- `@tool` for simple, stateless tools
- `BaseTool` for tools with configuration or state
- Descriptive docstring (the LLM uses it to choose the tool)
- `args_schema` with Pydantic for complex parameters
- Use `crewai_tools` built-in when possible
- Inject dependencies (API keys, URLs) via constructor
